Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.05,0:00:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫李奥纳多\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}My name is Leonardo,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.17,0:00:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,现在\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}and right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.99,0:00:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我和我的兄弟们正遇到大麻烦\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}my brothers and I are in a mess of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.73,0:00:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在一条散落着垃圾的小巷里 无路可退\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Our backs are up against the wall in some trash-strewn alley,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.48,0:00:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,被东区最强大的帮派逼到角落\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}cornered by the toughest street gang on the East Side.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.95,0:00:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧这些怪胎\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Look at the freaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.34,0:00:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,穿的什么蠢服装\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}What's with the dweeby costumes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.07,0:00:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,又不是万圣节\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}This ain't Halloween.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.54,0:00:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你们完蛋了 怪胎们\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}You're going down, freaks!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.22,0:00:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.06,0:00:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,没人敢惹我们紫龙帮\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Nobody messes with The Purple Dragons,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.21,0:00:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是穿着龟服的蠢货\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}especially wearing stupid turtle costumes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.67,0:00:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他错了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}He's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.66,0:00:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我们根本没穿衣服\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}We're not wearing costumes.
